						               													<description>A scenario, based on a classic Clint Eastwood Western.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The  mining  town  of  Lagos  a  remote  mountain  place in Inyo County. The local townsfolk fear the return of three notorious outlaws who they helped send to prison years ago, and when a mysterious gunfighter rides into town unannounced, the citizens of Lagos beg him for help. But the gunfighter, known only as &amp;ldquo;the  Stranger&amp;rdquo; is not here by coincidence. He has a mission of his own....&amp;#10;&amp;#10;To play this scenario, you&amp;rsquo;ll need 13 cowboy miniatures and a small Western town. There are a dozen characters in this game, each with a custom character card. Assign each player in your game the role of an Outlaw or a Citizen. There is also a card for the Stranger, but he will appear randomly throughout the story and may be controlled by either side.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Before the game, each player will be asked to revisit a decision   from earlier in the film, providing an opportunity for you to write a new ending to the movie!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
